ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-Order.-CREDIT_-Anton-Corbijn-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-Order.-CREDIT_-Anton-Corbijn-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-Order.-CREDIT_-Anton-Corbijn-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-order">New Order</a>宣布将重新发行 1986 年录音室专辑《Brotherhood》的豪华套装。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="457" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/new-order-power-corruption-and-lies-reissue-joy-division-interview-2764149"><b>“感觉就像我们正在改变世界”：新秩序的开创性“权力、腐败和谎言”</b></a></li></ul><p> New Order 的第四张专辑最初是通过 Factory Records 发行的，他们进一步深入研究了后朋克和电子音乐，将唱片的每一面划分为两种截然不同的声音氛围。</p><p>现在，名为“Brotherhood (Definitive Edition)”的限量版套装将庆祝这张开创性的专辑，并将于 11 月 22 日通过华纳音乐发行。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_fwXFLCA9f/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-gr